---
<section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background glow -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-accent-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-50"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-primary tracking-tight max-w-4xl leading-tight mb-8">
            Sites Ultrarrápidos que <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-primary to-accent-secondary">Transformam Visitas em Clientes</span>.<br />
            Sem Burocracia de Agências.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary max-w-2xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
            Desenvolvimento sob medida para negócios locais. Esqueça os templates genéricos e os formulários que ninguém responde. Acelere sua captação de leads direto para o seu WhatsApp.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
            <a href="#contato" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-accent-primary text-white font-semibold text-lg hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(59,130,246,0.5)] transition-all duration-300 w-full sm:w-auto text-center">
                Iniciar Projeto pelo WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a href="#portfolio" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-primary font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 w-full sm:w-auto text-center">
                Ver Portfólio de Conversão
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
